<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٨٨٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6333">الْمَكِّيُّ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1681">حَنْظَلَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ </a>قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2">أَصْحَابُنَا، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6333">الْمَكِّيِّ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span>،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«مِنَ الْفِطْرَةِ قَصُّ الشَّارِبِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>